------------------------------------------------------------
	EmoVoice (Emotional Speech Recognition)
------------------------------------------------------------	
	
	EmoVoice is an emotional speech recognizer implemented in the SSI framework. It comes with a pipeline (emovoice.pipeline) and an example model (emovoice.trainer). The user is encouraged to train a personalized model using the training GUI (modelui.exe).
	
	_RUN_EMOVOICE.bat :	
	
		Starts the recognition pipeline and a console application that receives and displays recognition results.
	
	_RUN_EMOTRAIN.bat :
	
		Starts the graphical interface that let you create your own emotional speech database.
	
